        * Have a strong statistical background. The position requires data mining / manipulation of data sets to extract timely, meaningful and impactful insights.
        * MS or PhD degree in a quantitative/ technical field from top tier university
        * Programming languages (C++, Java, Python)
        * Statistical modeling (R, SPSS, SAS)
        * Strong SQL and NoSQL experience
        * Ability to think creatively
        * Ability to traverse big picture as well as finer details
